text:
We were in New York for 3 days and used the 2 day pass which was incredibly cheaper than buying separate tickets.
We did the hop on bus tours-downtown, uptown and Harlem;
places of interest- Statue of Liberty and Ellis Island , 9/11 museum, Empire State Building and top of the rock and got our money’s worth and avoided the queues. As others have mentioned this may be even more worthwhile if u have a longer visit in New York for 3-7 days.
